==学术研究==
在攻读博士学位期间，任咏华研究高价金属钌和[[锇|锇]]的氧化化学，这一研究有助于研究生物体内[[细胞色素|细胞色素]]利用铁离子氧化碳-氢键，因为钌和锇与铁属于同一族<ref>{{cite journal|author=Chi Ming Che , Vivian Wing Wah Yam , Thomas C. W. Mak|title=A novel monooxoruthenium(V) complex containing a polydentate pyridyl amine ligand. Syntheses, reactivities, and x-ray crystal structure of [RuIII(N4O)(H2O)](ClO4)2|journal=J. Am. Chem. Soc.|year=1990|volume=112|issue=6|pages=2284–2291|doi=10.1021/ja00162a032|url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja00162a032|accessdate=2014-03-16|archive-date=2021-02-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209112546/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja00162a032|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | url=http://pubs.rsc.org/en/Content/ArticleLanding/1988/C3/c39880000100#!divAbstract | title=Metal–oxo photo-oxidants: photochemical oxidation of hydrocarbons by trans-dioxo complexes of ruthenium(VI) and osmium(VI) | author=Vivian Wing-Wah Yam,   Chi-Ming Che and    Wai-Tong Tang | journal=J. Chem. Soc., Chem. Commun. | year=1988 | pages=100-102 | doi=10.1039/C39880000100 | access-date=2014-03-16 | archive-date=2021-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209112551/https://pubs.rsc.org/en/Content/ArticleLanding/1988/C3/c39880000100#!divAbstract | dead-url=no }}</ref> 。

独立工作之后，任咏华主要的研究领域是[[化学传感器|化学传感器]]配合物和无机发光化学和材料。在化学传感器方面，她的课题组制备出可用作短序列DNA指示剂和检测[[溶菌酶|溶菌酶]]的有机金属配合物<ref>{{cite journal | url=http://www.pnas.org/content/103/52/19652.abstract?ijkey=22ea9a19500e589d99842063bcb0794bdd2832ea&keytype2=tf_ipsecsha | title=Single-stranded nucleic acid-induced helical self-assembly of alkynylplatinum(II) terpyridyl complexes | author=Cong Yu, Kenneth Hoi-Yiu Chan, Keith Man-Chung Wong, and Vivian Wing-Wah Yam | journal=Proc Natl Acad Sci USA | year=2006 | volume=103 | issue=52 | pages=19652–19657 | doi=10.1073/pnas.0604998104 | access-date=2014-03-18 | archive-date=2021-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209112602/https://www.pnas.org/content/103/52/19652.abstract?ijkey=22ea9a19500e589d99842063bcb0794bdd2832ea&keytype2=tf_ipsecsha | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | url=http://pubs.rsc.org/en/Content/ArticleLanding/2010/CC/c0cc02631j#!divAbstract | title=Aptamer-induced self-assembly of a NIR-emissive platinum(II) terpyridyl complex for label- and immobilization-free detection of lysozyme and thrombin | author=Yeung MCL, Wong KMC, Tsang YKT, Yam VWW | journal=Chem Commun | year=2010 | volume=46 | issue=41 | pages=7709–7711 | doi=10.1039/C0CC02631J | access-date=2014-03-18 | archive-date=2021-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209112601/https://pubs.rsc.org/en/Content/ArticleLanding/2010/CC/c0cc02631j#!divAbstract | dead-url=no }}</ref>。任咏华自伦敦访问回到香港之后，开始发光材料的研究。她的课题组制备很多新种类的有机金属发光体<ref>{{cite journal | url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/(SICI)1521-3773(19981102)37:20%3C2857::AID-ANIE2857%3E3.0.CO;2-G/abstract | title=Proof of potassium ions by luminescence signalling based on weak gold–gold interactions in dinuclear gold(I) complexes | author=Yam VWW, Li CK, Chan CL | journal=Angew Chem Int Ed | year=1998 | volume=37 | issue=20 | pages=2857–2859 | access-date=2014-03-18 | archive-date=2015-07-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705153729/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/(SICI)1521-3773(19981102)37:20%3C2857::AID-ANIE2857%3E3.0.CO;2-G/abstract | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ar0000758 | title=Molecular design of transition metal alkynyl complexes as building blocks for luminescent metal-based materials: Structural and photophysical aspects | author=Yam VWW | journal=Acc Chem Res | year=2002 | volume=35 | issue=7 | pages=555–563 | doi=10.1021/ar0000758 | access-date=2014-03-18 | archive-date=2021-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209112612/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ar0000758 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的课题组制备出溶液稳定的磷光材料和磷光剂，可以很方便地沉积在玻璃、塑料等各种表面上，可用在有机发光器件上<ref>{{cite journal | url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/anie.201206457/abstract;jsessionid=CF040B68AF04406DF29378FE84C9B85B.f03t02 | title=Dendritic Luminescent Gold(III) Complexes for Highly Efficient Solution-Processable Organic Light-Emitting Devices | author=Tang MC, Tsang DPK, Chan MM, Wong KMC, Yam VWW | journal=Angew Chem Int Ed Engl | year=2013 | volume=52 | issue=1 | pages=446–449 | doi=10.1002/anie.201206457 | access-date=2014-03-18 | archive-date=2015-07-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150705054441/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1002/anie.201206457/abstract;jsessionid=CF040B68AF04406DF29378FE84C9B85B.f03t02 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。近年来，任咏华还研究了非常规结构的发光材料，比如金属凝胶<ref>{{cite journal | url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja900895x | title=Unusual luminescence enhancement of metallogels of alkynylplatinum(II) 2,6-bis(N-alkylbenzimidazol-2′-yl)pyridine complexes upon a gel-to-sol phase transition at elevated temperatures | author=Tam AYY, Wong KMC, Yam VWW | journal=J Am Chem Soc | year=2009 | volume=131 | issue=17 | pages=6253–6260 | doi=10.1021/ja900895x | access-date=2014-03-18 | archive-date=2021-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209112713/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja900895x | dead-url=no }}</ref>、球状胶束和柱状纳米结构等<ref>{{cite journal | url=http://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja203920w | title=Supramolecular self-assembly of amphiphilic anionic platinum(II) complexes: A correlation between spectroscopic and morphological properties | author=Po C, Tam AYY, Wong KMC, Yam VWW | journal=J Am Chem Soc | year=2011 | volume=133 | issue=31 | pages=12136–12143. | doi=10.1021/ja203920w | access-date=2014-03-18 | archive-date=2021-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209112703/https://pubs.acs.org/doi/abs/10.1021/ja203920w | dead-url=no }}</ref>，通过控制材料的结构，能够得到性能更好的材料。

至2013年，任咏华发表了347篇期刊论文，申请了29项[[专利|专利]]，撰写6篇专著章节，出版了2部专著。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://hub.hku.hk/cris/rp/rp00822/publications.html?open=journal | title=Yam, VWW Publications | publisher=HKU | accessdate=2014-03-18 | archive-date=2021-02-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210209112631/http://hub.hku.hk/cris/rp/rp00822/publications.html?open=journal | dead-url=no }}</ref>

